{"product":{"id":8567457153175,"title":"Urban Platter Shirataki Konjac Noodles, 270g | Zero Calorie | Fat-Free | Gluten-Free | Low Carb | Keto | Ready to Use","body_html":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIndia's Favourite Zero-Calorie Noodles — Keto, Low-Carb \u0026amp; Ready to Use\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eUrban Platter Shirataki Konjac Noodles are made from the konjac root — a Japanese superfood renowned for its glucomannan fibre content. With virtually zero calories, zero fat, and zero gluten, these noodles are the go-to choice for anyone on a keto, low-carb, diabetic-friendly, or weight-loss diet.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eZero Calories:\u003c\/strong\u003e Virtually calorie-free — eat guilt-free in any portion\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eFat-Free \u0026amp; Gluten-Free:\u003c\/strong\u003e Perfect for keto, paleo, and gluten-intolerant diets\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eLow Carb:\u003c\/strong\u003e Ideal for diabetics and anyone managing blood sugar\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHigh in Glucomannan Fibre:\u003c\/strong\u003e Supports digestive health and keeps you feeling full longer\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eReady to Use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Pre-cooked and packed in water — rinse, drain, and cook in minutes\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eVersatile:\u003c\/strong\u003e Use in stir-fries, soups, ramen, pasta dishes, or cold noodle salads\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to Use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Open pack, drain and rinse thoroughly under cold water. Dry-fry in a pan for 2 minutes to remove moisture. Add directly to your recipe — soups, stir-fries, or as a pasta substitute.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eStorage:\u003c\/strong\u003e Store in a cool, dry place. Best consumed immediately after opening.\u003c\/p\u003e","vendor"